oracle-watchdog (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Monitor mode: Consul session heartbeat on Oracle nodes
  * Agent mode: Watches for missing sessions and triggers OCI restart
  * Self-healing design: never crashes on connection issues
  * Prometheus metrics for monitoring
  * OpenTelemetry tracing support

